    2256 "Xx"
    2257 "Xx"
    2258 "Xx"
    2259 "Wonju is a key road-junction city nestled in a mountain basin of central Korea.\n\nHistorical Note:\nThe Wonju-Chipyongni area was denied to the enemy by the heroic stand of UN Forces in Jan. - Feb. 1951."
    2260 "Xx"
